  ($u96$Collection / All Beds$u96$, $u97$Amy Engineered Wood Queen Size Box Storage Bed In Classic Walnut Finish$u97$, $u98$Urban Ladder$u98$, $u99$Crush Sale — Up to 70% OFF! Shop Now$u99$, 12, NULL, $u100$2$u100$, $u101$1$u101$, $u102$90$u102$, $u103$28.55 kg$u103$, $u104$Sleep smarts and storage smarts. The sleek frame and linear pattern of our Amy storage bed makes it the perfect fit for any contemporary home. The headboard features two open shelves for all your bedtime essentials. A closed shutter ensures that any clutter can be effortlessly concealed. Made from Engineered Wood Please refer to images for dimension details$u104$, NULL, $u105$Engineered Wood$u105$, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 15999, $u106$https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/g1Zp4RA_iqu-1.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/2Gfrd-53KLM-2.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/nEEC3ueo2Yg-3.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/22aRC_Vsc3p-4.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/-KAIZLNF3s5-5.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/QyYtLdG_j6L-6.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/JiN46rhSlki-7.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/s3CqSfg7Lc4-8.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/g1Zp4RA_iqu-1.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/150x0/2Gfrd-53KLM-2.jpg$u106$, $u107$https://www.urbanladder.com/product/amy-engineered-wood-queen-size-box-s